headline: 5 Revealing Analyst Questions From Expedia’s Q2 Earnings Call
summary: Expedia’s second quarter results were shaped by a robust performance in its B2B and international businesses, offsetting continued softness in the U.S. leisure travel market. Management pointed to resilience among higher-end consumers and strong execution of strategic priorities, including investments in supply partnerships and loyalty initiatives.
